(39, 'Purchasing and Inventory Control: Defines the processes for 1) requesting, ordering and receipt of supplies, 2) the selection of approved suppliers, 3) acceptance/rejection criteria for purchased items, 4) safe handling; 5) storage; inventory control system; 6) monitoring and handling of expired consumables ', 'Purchasing and Inventory Control: Defines the processes for 1) requesting, ordering and receipt of supplies, 2) the selection of approved suppliers, 3) acceptance/rejection criteria for purchased items, 4) safe handling; 5) storage; inventory control system; 6) monitoring and handling of expired consumables ', '', '', ''),
